      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2008 Porsche Cayman S offers a masterclass in mid-engine balance. Powered by a 3.4L flat-six with VarioCam Plus, the powerplant is mated to a precise 6-speed manual transaxle, ensuring an engaging powerband and linear torque delivery. The chassis architecture provides a low polar moment of inertia, translating to exceptional rotational agility and communicative feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. Mechanical highlights include four-piston monoblock calipers over vented rotors for consistent thermal management and a rigid subframe that maintains suspension geometry under high lateral loads. This example is mechanically sorted with a documented service history, representing a high-performance platform ready for the enthusiast who values tactile engagement and engineering pedigree.",
